Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Does this feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:35.89,Episode Title,EpisodeTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fad(939,810)}"The Consequences of What Must Be Done"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.80,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off than out\N in the open back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.79,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a chance he'll \Ndisappear if we just buy time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:55.18,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,They probably offered all three \Nof our lives to summon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:00.01,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,He'll likely keep rampaging \Nuntil he kills us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.99,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Then if we break the barrier \Nand reunite with the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:04.83,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos fights by summoning \Ncountless heroic spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.06,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,According to the legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:15.07,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,We should consider it likely that there's \Nsomething going on outside the barrier, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.57,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to do something \Nabout him on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.62,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to resist if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.17,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if you two can match up \Nto me in this situation anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.95,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we hadn't even started yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.88,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,This is miasma from the demon \Nthat drains your life force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.80,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,See how even a succubus suffers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:03:00.15,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're human, it must\N be quite hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:04.70,Main,Rukia,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.97,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.22,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,The more you move, the worse you'll suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.47,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.49,Main,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:45.49,Main,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy anyone who \Nthreatens Basara-sama's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.04,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Banishing Shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.68,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. This is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.03,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.29,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.17,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.30,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.58,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't pass out just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.59,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,At least not until you've \Nwatched your cute little sister die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.09,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.02,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.60,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.29,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.69,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who went after \NRukia-neesama and Yuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.34,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,M-My hand! My...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.52,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.87,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,After harming both of them, \Nyou went after Kurumi-san, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.62,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-san is my precious to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.83,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.21,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,A-A lowly succubus dares to—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.88,Main,Admirath,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.26,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.26,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You almost called me your \Ntoy just now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.81,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.02,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.48,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,To think you tried to attack Kurumi-san \Nin her sleep right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.75,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,You went a bit too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.47,Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.50,Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Lars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.76,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, pulling stunts like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:35.31,Main,Lars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourselves, you puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.31,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.71,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Ramsus-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:43.19,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to worry about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:47.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,then think of some way to \Ndeal with that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.76,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with him? How...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.95,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.49,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,The reason Chaos can't leave that space
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:08:00.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is that gravity magic is \Nacting on the space around it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:04.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,creating a dimensional \Nfault that he can't cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.96,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:12.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a gravity-based attack might be able \Nto seal him into another dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.32,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.41,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,A black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.82,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Create that black hole from before \Nonce more and suck him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:27.55,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,So, it has to be for only a few short \Nmoments, but please stop him from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:28.73,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.30,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,In that opening, Mio will need \Nto create her black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.74,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll push him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.08,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.46,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, I'm going to unleash my limiters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.89,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,This time, all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.26,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.09,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to do it for the \Nfirst time at a crucial moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.38,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.88,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.49,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,When this is all over, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.00,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.38,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.40,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:17.66,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,On my pride as the Demon Lord, \NI promise to stop him in his tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:29.13,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think a relic of the past like \Nyou can destroy us that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.15,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.00,Italics,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.47,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.73,Italics,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.84,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.59,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Into another dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.17,Main,Council,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.81,Main,Council,0000,0000,0000,,They defeated Chaos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.49,Main,Madonis,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll have to use our last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:11.92,Main,Madonis,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone in there \Nshall be turned to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To our victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.55,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.85,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,The older sister makes \Nher gallant appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.09,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,But it's your fault, old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:37.11,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to dispose of my Leo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:41.69,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was letting you all live \Nout of the profound kindness of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:47.09,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long are you going \Nto keep hiding there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.95,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Come out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.78,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you prefer to be dragged out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.45,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you noticed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.84,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What a scary young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.55,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I thought heroic spirits were \Nsent to Wildart, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:06.09,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are an incredible god of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.72,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one shaking over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:12.09,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd completely \Neliminated my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:15.75,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I have a very strong woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.36,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not very friendly, Mr. War God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.83,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to kill \Nthese old men, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:27.61,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you left me with all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.68,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:34.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,fed inside of you to give \Noff such a monstrous aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:40.04,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk about \Nothers, Mr. War God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:44.01,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a dragon around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:48.31,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,One of the ancient, high-ranking dragons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.21,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,But that solves the mystery of how
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,your son is able to use \Nthat dimensional shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:56.89,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:01.61,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he's inherited your \Nblood. Right, Mr. War God?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:05.44,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.33,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should take care of that boy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.52,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.95,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to remain no more than \Ninsurance until the end this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.10,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good, Mr. War God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.12,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to be like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:24.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll only have more people I'll \Nneed to eliminate for Leo-kun's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.85,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?! Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:38.59,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,My, I'm a bit impressed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.92,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you managed to make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.61,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.22,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.74,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here for the \Nsame reason as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.61,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.23,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.74,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you didn't come on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.62,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.84,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mr. War God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.17,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,This young lady doesn't \Nintend to cause a stir here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:10.01,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, may I call you "Basara-kun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:13.14,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to get along awfully well with Lars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:18.26,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Now all the old men on the council are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:21.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I hope you start getting along \Nwith Leo-kun more, as well, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.13,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.80,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later, Mr. War God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.53,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.52,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.79,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Leohart's older sister, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.05,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.91,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,She wiped out the entire council in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.64,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, pulling these stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:50.46,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to come this far, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.00,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can start seeing our path to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.61,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,This time the results turned out rather well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:16:00.31,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly, it was all down to the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:04.04,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to fight against \NLeohart all thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:08.57,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,and I managed to defeat that demon \Nonly because I got Ramsus-san's help
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and cooperation from both Mio and Leohart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.27,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.89,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.33,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:22.33,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:27.11,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's over for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:33.49,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope this finally manages to free \NMio from the demon realm's squabbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.70,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.60,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Just as that young lady said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the council's all gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.80,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this, Leo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.16,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,It was like this when I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:56.31,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,None of the women are able \Nto reveal much at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.41,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clue what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.19,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,This smells familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.04,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,This fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.61,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.91,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,This is the smell of perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:16.89,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if he killed Belphegor, \Nthen the council's influence would wane,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and war would die down in the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.88,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.01,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Then why would he need to fight Leo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.73,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,If he missed a step,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:30.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,it could have cost his precious \Ncomrades their lives, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.67,Italics,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:40.78,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Resolving this isn't as simple \Nas just eliminating the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.58,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:46.21,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we proposed peace by \Noffering up Belphegor's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:50.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones we surpassed would \Nbe even more wary of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.51,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Basara risked \Nhis life against Leohart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:18:01.06,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Unveiling the council's plot and \Ncrushing it gives us a path to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.11,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,If the demon realm's wars dwindle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:08.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be even fewer people going \Nout of their way to pursue Mio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.61,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:12.70,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bad deal for you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.44,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,Your son has changed the \Nhistory of the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.63,Main,Ramsus,0000,0000,0000,,All for the sake of one precious sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.17,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Leo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.25,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,I might have messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.09,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.98,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.25,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Leo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.02,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Leo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.33,Main,Liala,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're back in your room, \NI'll give you all the praise you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.66,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Elder sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.53,Main,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you actually pulled it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.09,Main,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,Whom are you planning to fight after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:04.36,Main,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't even believe \Nyou made me go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.54,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.49,Main,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,You've already come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:10.55,Main,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it up well, Basacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.44,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.93,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.98,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already long...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:15.75,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.42,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.21,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.76,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Warm me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:27.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.63,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:42.77,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.37,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:51.88,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing for cold \Nnights is hot, wet action!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.02,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're like that year-round!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.08,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi, that outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.88,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not what you think! \NMaria made me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.78,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Naughty girls who make excuses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.15,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:05.30,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.96,Main,Basacchi,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:07.82,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.78,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.28,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:17.72,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.64,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.36,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Basara...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.18,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair only Onee gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.18,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.33,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Basara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.52,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a nice look, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.69,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for Kurumi-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:40.50,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:43.19,Main,Zest,0000,0000,0000,,Basara-sama, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.89,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.20,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.72,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,He's my Basara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:56.93,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.82,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine! Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:00.05,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.46,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:05.61,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll relieve you all together!
